==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nominee
<hw>Nom`i*nee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Nominate</er>, and <er>-ee</er>.]</ety> <def>A person named, or
designated, by another, to any office, duty, or position; one nominated,
or proposed, by others for office or for election to office. One remains
a <ex>nominee</ex> until one has been elected or has assumed the
office.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nominor</ent>⟦br⟧
